<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wqt ạlmḥn mạlqạsẖ ạ̉ḥn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (wqt ạlmḥn mạlqạsẖ ạ̉ḥn .. mnk ạ̹nt yḍmny
 tyjy ạ̉kyd wạbqy̱ sʿyd .. wạḥs byk btḥbny)2
 (tsmʿ wtsẖfy wtʿṭy wykfy .. wyfyḍ klạmk bạlḥnạn
 wạlqạk ạ̉mạmy rạḥty wslạmy .. nwry wnbʿ mn ạlạ̉mạn)2
 nwry wnbʿ mn ạlạ̉mạn
 2- (kl ạlly fạt mn tʿzyạt .. ysẖhd lwʿdk ạlạ̉myn
 ḥy bwjwd ymḥy ạlsdwd .. wyfk qyd ạlmtʿbyn)2
 (lạms wjwdk kẖyrk wjwdk .. rgẖm ạlṣʿạb ạlly tzyd
 bạsẖhd lḥbk wḥnạn qlbk .. tẓhr tmly bfjr jdyd)2
 tẓhr tmly bfjr jdyd</lyrics>
<hymn_number>298</hymn_number>
<author>hạny ạ̉nys, ạ̉lbyr smyr</author>
</song>